social_posts.post_text: Congratulations to @tonymcewing1 on your retirement! Three decades on morning television in SoCal— looking forward to seeing what’s next for you!  We’ll miss you! ❤️🙌🏽

Programming note! Join @brookeonair and me 4-6 am! (Before you say it … We know… it’s early 😂) Welcoming @_melvinrobert and @jennlahmers to the @foxla family 6-9 am! Then your favs @araksyakarapetyan and @sandraendotv 9-11am! #gooddayla @foxla
Celebrating Asian American Pacific Islander Heritage Month with great pride and gratitude for my late parents ❤️🇺🇸🇵🇭🙏🏽 #aapiheritagemonth #celebratediversity #foxla #gooddayla

embrace love, celebrate diversity, and stand as allies. 🏳️‍🌈 This morning on @foxla we’re recognizing the contributions of the @NoH8Campaign - which has been fighting discrimination and tirelessly working towards inclusion and #equalityforall for the past 15 years! #NOH8

The majestic Banyan tree on Lahaina’s Front Street has provided beautiful memories to so many for 150 years.  This pic was taken a year ago.  It was charred in the massive fire, but I was so happy to hear this morning that there is hope it MAY survive 🙏🏽❤️ The Aloha Spirit will always be strong! #maui
Our @fox11creative team did such a Spook-tacular job dressing up the studio for Halloween! 👻 💀 🧟 They are SCARY talented!  Happy Halloween everyone! 🎃 @foxla #happyhalloween

I was 17 when I decided to join the military.  At first, it was mainly for a scholarship as my parents were putting five boys through college and couldn’t afford it.  But I had invaluable experiences while serving and gained lifelong friends.  Turned out to be one the most consequential and best decisions of my life! ⚓️ I am forever indebted.  Thank you veterans and your families for your sacrifice! Honored to have served with you 🇺🇸 #veteransday #GoNavy

Who wore it better ?? @araksyakarapetyan and I made ugly Christmas sweaters for each other 9 years ago! She won that contest - but I’m ready for a rematch! We pulled them out of the back of the closet for the @foxla holiday party! Happy holidays! 🎄🎅 🕎
